config SND_HY310_TRID_AUDIO_BRIDGE
	tristate "HY310 Trident audio bridge"
	depends on SOUND && SND && OF && ARCH_SUNXI
	select DMA_SHARED_BUFFER
	help
	  Raw ALSA audio-bridge driver for the HY310 projector on Allwinner H713.
	  This is a port of the stock snd_alsa_trid module used for speaker,
	  bridge, delayline and S/PDIF routing.

	  The implementation is reverse-engineered from stock snd_alsa_trid.ko
	  with IDA Pro and adapted for Linux 6.16 without vendor ION APIs.

	  Say Y or M if you have an HY310-class H713 device.
